description: Simple SCCS
json:
{
  "analysisId": 1,
  "description": "Simple SCCS",
  "getDbSccsDataArgs": {
    "useCustomCovariates": false,
    "deleteCovariatesSmallCount": 100,
    "studyStartDate": "",
    "studyEndDate": "",
    "customCovariateIds": "",
    "attr_class": "args"
  },
  "createSccsEraDataArgs": {
    "naivePeriod": 365,
    "firstOutcomeOnly": false,
    "covariateSettings": {
      "includeCovariateIds": "exposureId",
      "label": "Exposure of interest",
      "stratifyById": true,
      "start": 0,
      "addExposedDaysToStart": false,
      "end": 0,
      "addExposedDaysToEnd": true,
      "firstOccurrenceOnly": false,
      "allowRegularization": false,
      "attr_class": "covariateSettings"
    },
    "ageSettings": {
      "includeAge": false,
      "ageKnots": 5,
      "allowRegularization": false,
      "attr_class": "ageSettings"
    },
    "seasonalitySettings": {
      "includeSeasonality": false,
      "seasonKnots": 5,
      "allowRegularization": false,
      "attr_class": "seasonalitySettings"
    },
    "eventDependentObservation": false,
    "attr_class": "args"
  },
  "fitSccsModelArgs": {
    "prior": {
      "priorType": "laplace",
      "variance": 1,
      "exclude": null,
      "graph": null,
      "neighborhood": null,
      "useCrossValidation": true,
      "forceIntercept": false,
      "attr_class": "cyclopsPrior"
    },
    "control": {
      "maxIterations": 1000,
      "tolerance": 1e-006,
      "convergenceType": "gradient",
      "autoSearch": true,
      "fold": 10,
      "lowerLimit": 0.01,
      "upperLimit": 20,
      "gridSteps": 10,
      "minCVData": 100,
      "cvRepetitions": 1,
      "noiseLevel": "quiet",
      "threads": 1,
      "seed": null,
      "resetCoefficients": false,
      "startingVariance": 0.1,
      "useKKTSwindle": false,
      "tuneSwindle": 10,
      "selectorType": "byPid",
      "initialBound": 2,
      "maxBoundCount": 5,
      "attr_class": "cyclopsControl"
    },
    "attr_class": "args"
  },
  "attr_class": "sccsAnalysis"
}
